<p>
<note n="0804010" resp="#resp2" type="mod" target="#nkr_note_mod_0804010">唯＝惟【宋】【元】【明】【宮】下同</note>
<note n="0805002" resp="#resp2" type="mod" target="#nkr_note_mod_0805002">類＋（等）【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note>
<note n="0805004" resp="#resp2" type="mod" target="#nkr_note_mod_0805004">菉＝綠【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note>
<note n="0807004" resp="#resp2" type="mod" target="#nkr_note_mod_0807004">廛＝纏【宋】【元】【明】，＝厘【宮】【聖】</note>
<note n="0808001" resp="#resp2" type="mod" target="#nkr_note_mod_0808001">〔與受〕二字－【宋】</note>
